{"id": "vos016", "name": "Audio_H1001_702_12_29_4", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Nora, did you find him...?\n"}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>No... I've searched all over the city. He's nowhere to be found. I can't imagine he'd go to another Node.\nMr. Jackson's vitals are normal, which means he's still alive. But... where is he...</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "... What about here? Have you searched this location?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>Here... what do you mean?</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Here. If the transmission coordinates Miss PAFF set up were to bring them back here, then perhaps he's located beneath our feet. Or... above our heads.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......!!\nAbove? I didn't search there, but... If he's really there... he's in a lot of danger.</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Isn't that full of Architects that Vanessa is controlling? If we connect there...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "I'll go! If anything happens, I still have the virus...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Aroma-chan!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "Using the virus on those bastards would be quite a waste. I hope we can stick to the plan.\nWe'll use the same formation; Miss Wildcat and I will provide cover. Miss PAFF, leave the virus here and we'll go up to look around.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>... Okay, that's what we'll do.</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["MetalImpact", "Object Crashes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "What was that?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "Not good! Outside! A whole bunch of Architects!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Eh? Ehhh? What're we gonna do...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "... <i>*yawn*</i>... Perfect timing... Almost like they knew...? \nSuccessor! You and the others outside stop them from busting in here!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "You got it!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... We're not there yet? Feels like we've already walked for some time now.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Almost there, it's right ahead.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "If I can let Nora know your location in the OS space, perhaps she's got a way to bring you back to reality...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "We found Shannon's consciousness stuck in here before, she said that if we brought her body to the same location, there's a possibility that they could be reconnected. I know your body has already... but... \n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Really?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry... after all of this, I never had a chance to tell you, I...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Oh... I wanted to wait until you recovered in Kyuu Hou Kai to tell you this... Now, running into you here, I don't know where to begin...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Just say it.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I regret... my decision to leave you, so much. It's been like this these past few years. I didn't do that because I hated you, I... I always regarded that decision as a punishment I gave myself. I couldn't stop all of this from happening, couldn't protect the people around me... I feel like I don't deserve to be happy.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "But I... I didn't think how it would affect you. I didn't think how much suffering it would cause you. The people I care about, the one's still alive, they're the most important thing in my life. The time I spent with you was filled with happiness. Thank you.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Yeah, me too.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "We'll definitely think of a way to get you out of here. After all this is over, let's try to...\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\"><i>X͟͝e͟n̛͜͜͞o̸͢ǹ͘҉͡...... Xenon...... can you hear me?</i></font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...... Wait a second, do you hear that? It's PAFF's voice! I think we're there!\nPAFF! It's me! I hear you!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenon! Finally connected to you! There's a strong signal near you causing interference. I can't get there. You've got to get out of there now!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Hold on! I found Sherry! She's right in front of me!\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Sherry...? What are you talking about? You're getting closer to the Library! It'll be too dangerous if you get close to Vanessa's core! \n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "I don't know what you're seeing, but there's nothing here besides Architect consciousnesses. You've got to turn around, head toward my voice!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon... you hear that too?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Don't take the bait... It sounds like the voice I heard before. It will do whatever it takes; all there is in that direction, is an evil presence.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Oh...\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenon! Neko and Neumann can't hold on for much longer! Your connection time is almost up! If you don't leave soon and you lose connection there, you won't be able to get back!\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Come on, we've got to keep moving forward.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Sherry...\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon...?\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... I... How did you know about the other's situation?\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...Eh?\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "You said you've been here all along and didn't know what's going on outside... How'd you know we were at A.R.C. in Node 08?\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n... Is now... really the time to talk about that?\nWe've got to hurry up...\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "Draws Gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......!!\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...... Answer me.\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon... you... you don't trust me?\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Ugh...\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenon! Nora said the source of the interfering signal is right next to you! Whatever you see, you cannot continue forward!\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Didn't you say... you w-w-wanted(̷̢͘̕q̕a̴̷̛̕z̵̡̢͜҉to find a way to get me out of here......?\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... <i>*sob*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 63, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "After w-w-wer҉̕͘͞)̷̸̡͘~͏͜get out... After it's all over... W-W-W-We... should tryf̶̧̨͜n̶̡͡҉p̡̧̀͢͟>̷̧͘͜t̸̡Ý̢......\n"}, {"id": 64, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">If I can't let this go, I'll never move forward...</font>\n"}, {"id": 65, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["EMP_01", "Gunshot"], "content": ""}, {"id": 66, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...... Simon......`̸̢̨̕͏h̴̡̛̀́p̕͟{̵̸̴͞S-S-S-Sorry...\n...... I love you......</font>\n"}, {"id": 67, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Ivy_Hacking", "Signal Disappears"], "content": ""}, {"id": 68, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...... <i>*sob* ... *sob*</i>...\n<font size=\"3.6\">URRGGHHAAAAAAAHHH!!!!!</font>\n"}, {"id": 69, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Nora……どう……？\n"}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ダメ……\n町中を探してみたけれど、どこにも見当たらない。\nでも、他のNodeへ行ったとも考えにくい。\nJacksonさんのバイタルサインには何の問題もない……つまり生きてはいる。\nいったいどこに……</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……ここはどうだね？\n探したかね？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>ここ……？どういう意味？</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "「ここ」さ。\n攻撃された瞬間にMissPAFFが転送した座標がこの場所であれば、彼も我々の足元……もしくは頭上にいるのではないかね？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……！！\n上……は、確かに探してない……\nでも、もし本当にそこにいるんだとしたら、Jacksonさんはかなり危険な状態。</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "上ってVanessaの操縦するロボットだらけなんだよね！？\nそんなところに入っちゃったら……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "私が行く！\nもし何かあっても、私ならウィルスを持ってる……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Aromaっち！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "やつらにウィルスを使ってしまうのはいささか大げさすぎるのではないかね？\n可能であれば作戦通りに進めたいところだな。\n先ほどと同じフォーメーションで行こう。\n私と野良猫のお嬢さんが掩護する。\nMissPAFFは、ウィルスはここに置いて捜索を行ってくれ。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……そうしましょう。</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["MetalImpact", "物がぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "何の音だね？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "やばい！外に！大量のアーキテクトが！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "えっ！？えええ！？\nどっどうしよう……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "っチ……最悪のタイミングだな……\nいや、今だからこそなのか……？\n2代目よ！外の者たちと協力して奴らを阻止してくれたまえ！\n決してここに侵入させてはならない！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "了解！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……まだ着かないのか？\nもうだいぶ歩いた気がするんだが。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "もうすぐだよ。\nもうそこだから。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Noraにお前の位置を知らせることができれば、お前を現実世界へ連れて帰る方法が見つかるかもしれない……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "作戦の途中でShannonの意識を見つけることができたんだ。\nNoraが言うには、もしあいつの身体をその場所へ連れて行くことができれば、また意識と身体を繋げることができるかもしれないと。\nお前の身体はもう……あれだが……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……そっか。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry……色々あってずっと伝えられなかったことがあるんだ……\n俺は……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……っ……\n本当は、玖凰會での治療が終わったら言おうと思ってた。\nでも……実際にお前を目の前にすると……何から話したらいいのかわからなくなるな……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……うん。聞くよ。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "俺は……ずっと後悔してた。\nあの時、お前を手放してしまったことを……この数年ずっと……\nお前が憎かったわけじゃない。\n俺は……何も防げなかった自分に……大切な人を守れなかった自分に幸せになる価値はないと……\nだからこれはそんな自分に対する罰だって思おうとしてたんだ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "だが……俺はお前のことを何も考えてなかった。\nお前が苦しむなんて考えてもみなかったんだ。\n本当に大切なのはまだ生きてる人間なのに。\n今ならわかる。\nお前と一緒に過ごした時間は本当に幸せだった。ありがとう……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……うん。あたしもだよ。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "必ずお前を救い出す方法を見つける。\nすべてが終わったらまた……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\"><i>X͟͝e͟n̛͜͜͞o̸͢ǹ͘҉͡……Xenonさん……聞こえる？</i></font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……待て。聞こえたか？\nPAFFの声だ！着いたみたいだ！\nPAFF！俺だ！聞こえるか！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenonさん！やっと繋がった！\nそっちのすぐそばにとても強いシグナルがあってそっちへは行けないの！\nとにかく！早くそこを離れて！\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "待ってくれ！Sherryを見つけたんだ！\nここに！俺のすぐ目の前にいる！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Sherryさんが……？\n何を言っているの？\nXenonさん！そこはLibraryのすぐ近くなの！\nもしVanessaに近づいてしまったら大変なことに！\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenonさん！あなたに今何が見えているのか私には分からない。\nでも、そこにはアーキテクトの意識以外何もない！\nはやく！私の声方へ！こっち！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……聞こえた？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "これは罠。騙されないで。\nいつもこうなんだ……色んな手を使ってあたしをあっちへおびき寄せようとする。\nでも、向こうへ進んでも感じるのは徐々に強くなる殺意だけ。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "う……っ\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenonさん！NEKOとNeumannさんもこれ以上は耐えられそうにない！\nそれにXenonさんが接続できる時間の限界も迫ってる！\n急いで！そこで接続が切れてしまったらもう戻ってこれない！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "行こう。足を止めないで。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……Sherry……\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……？\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……なぁ……なんでみんなのことを知ってた……？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……は？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ずっとここにいて、外のことは何もわからないって言ってたよな……？\nなら、なんで俺たちがNode08のA.R.C.にいることを知ってた？\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n……今は……そんな話をしてる場合じゃないでしょ。\n急がないと……\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "銃を構える"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……答えるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……あたしが信じられない？\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……っく……\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenonさん！\n私たちの邪魔をしているシグナルはあなたのすぐ隣から発してるものだってNoraが！\n何が見えたとしてもついて行ったらダメ！\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "ここから……脱脱脱出(̷̢͘̕q̕a̴̷̛̕z̵̡̢͜҉ｽｽスル方法を考えてくれるって言ったじゃん……\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……っ……\n"}, {"id": 63, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "帰ったらﾗr҉̕͘͞)̷̸̡͘~͏͜ﾗ……すべてが終わったら……ﾏﾏマﾀ……やり直ｵｵf̶̧̨͜n̶̡͡҉p̡̧̀͢͟>̷̧͘͜t̸̡Ý̢そう……っテ……\n"}, {"id": 64, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">手放さない限り……前に進めない……</font>\n"}, {"id": 65, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["EMP_01", "銃声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 66, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……Simon……`̸̢̨̕͏h̴̡̛̀́p̕͟{̵̸̴͞ｺﾞゴごメ……ん……\n……愛しテる……</font>\n"}, {"id": 67, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Ivy_Hacking", "シグナルが消える"], "content": ""}, {"id": 68, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……っ……あ……\n<font size=\"3.6\">ああああああああ！！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 69, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Nora，找到了嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>不……我已經找遍城裡所有地方了，到處都沒有，也很難想像他會跑到其他 Node 去。\nJackson 先生的身體生命跡象還正常，代表他還活著。但……到底在哪……</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "……這裡呢？找過了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>這裡……？什麼意思？</i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "這裡啊，如果被攻擊的瞬間 Miss PAFF 傳送的座標是傳回這裡，那他也許就在我們腳下，或者是……我們頭上。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……！！\n上面嗎？我的確還沒找過那裡，但……如果真的在那裡，那 Jackson 先生的處境很危險。</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "上面不是都是 Vanessa 操控的機器人嗎？現在連進去的話……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "我去吧！如果有什麼萬一，我還有病毒……\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Aroma 醬！\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "用病毒對抗那些傢伙有點太小題大作了，可以的話還是希望計畫能夠順利進行呢。\n用一樣的陣容吧，我跟野貓小姐做掩護，Miss PAFF 把病毒留在這裡，上去做搜索。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>……就這麼辦吧。</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["MetalImpact", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "什麼聲音？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "不好啦！外面！一大堆的建造者！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "咦？咦咦？怎、怎麼辦……\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "呿……偏偏在這種時候……不，正因為是這種時候嗎……？\n第二代！你和外面的人去阻止它們，不能讓它們闖進這裡！\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "好！\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……還沒到嗎？感覺已經走了一陣子了。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "快到了，就在前面。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "如果能讓 Nora 知道妳在 OS 空間的位置，也許她會有把妳帶回現實的方法……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "先前我們在行動中找到了 Shannon 被困住的意識，她說若能把身體帶回同一個地方，也許能有重新連結的可能。雖然妳的身體已經……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……是嗎。\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry……遭遇到那麼多事，我一直沒機會跟妳說，我……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "唔……本來打算等妳在玖凰會被醫好後就跟妳說這些話的，現在遇到妳反而又不知道從哪裡說起了……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……說吧。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我很後悔……當初離開妳的決定，這些年都是。我並不是因為恨妳才這麼做的，我……一直把這個決定當成給自己的懲罰，沒能阻止那些事情發生、沒能保護身邊的人……我覺得這樣的自己沒有幸福的資格。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "但……我卻忽略了妳，沒有想到這樣也是在讓妳受苦。真正重要的，是還活著的人，我現在懂這點了。跟妳在一起的時光，真的很幸福，謝謝妳。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……嗯，我也是。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我們一定會想出救妳出去的方法，等這一切都結束後，我們再重新……\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\"><i>X͟͝e͟n̛͜͜͞o̸͢ǹ͘҉͡……Xenon……聽得到嗎……？</i></font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……等等，妳有聽到嗎？是 PAFF 的聲音！好像真的到了！\nPAFF！是我！聽到了！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenon！總算連上你了！你附近有好強的訊號干擾，我過不去，總之快點離開那裡！\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "等一下！我找到 Sherry 了！就在我面前！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Sherry……？你在說什麼？你正一步步在往 Library 靠近啊！要是接近 Vanessa 的核心就危險了！\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "我不知道你現在看到什麼，但這邊除了建造者的意識外沒有別的東西了，快點回頭，往我聲音的方向走！\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……你也聽到了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "別上當，那是……跟我聽到的聲音一樣，它會用盡各種方法，如果往那個方向走，感覺到的只有越來越濃的殺意。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenon！NEKO 跟 Neumann 先生已經快撐不下去了！你連線的時間也快到了！如果不快點離開，在那個地方斷線的話你就回不來了啊！\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "走吧，我們必須繼續往前。\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……Sherry……\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……？\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……我……問妳，妳是怎麼知道大家的事的？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……咦？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳說妳一直待在這裡，不知道外面的情況……妳是怎麼知道我們人現在在 Node 08 的 A.R.C. 大廳的？\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n……現在……不是說這些的時候了吧？我們得快點……\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "舉槍"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……！！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……回答我。\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon……你……不相信我嗎？\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……唔……\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenon！Nora 說干擾的訊號源就在你旁邊！不管你看到什麼都不要往前！\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 61, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你不是說……要要(̷̢͘̕q̕a̴̷̛̕z̵̡̢͜҉幫我想出離開這裡的方法嗎……？\n"}, {"id": 62, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……嗚……\n"}, {"id": 63, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "回去以以r҉̕͘͞)̷̸̡͘~͏͜以後……一切都結束後……我我我們……再重f̶̧̨͜n̶̡͡҉p̡̧̀͢͟>̷̧͘͜t̸̡Ý̢新……\n"}, {"id": 64, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">不放下就無法前進……</font>\n"}, {"id": 65, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["EMP_01", "槍聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 66, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……Simon……`̸̢̨̕͏h̴̡̛̀́p̕͟{̵̸̴͞對對……不起……\n……我愛你……</font>\n"}, {"id": 67, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Ivy_Hacking", "訊號消失"], "content": ""}, {"id": 68, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……嗚嗚……\n<font size=\"3.6\">嗚嗚啊啊啊啊啊！！！</font>\n"}, {"id": 69, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "Nora 씨, 찾으셨나요...?\n"}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>아직...\n이미 모든 곳을 뒤져봤지만, 전부 그곳에는 없었습니다. 그리고 다른 Node로 갔을리도 없고...\nJackson 씨의 생체 반응은 정상으로 표시되고 있으니 아직 살아있다는 뜻이겠죠...하지만... 대체 어디에 있는 건지...</i>\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "......이곳은? 찾아보신 겁니까?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>이곳이라니......? 무슨 뜻이죠? </i>\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "이곳 말입니다.\n만약 공격을 당한 순간 Miss PAFF가 전송 좌표를 이곳으로 제대로 설정해뒀다면... 우리들의 발 밑에... 혹은 그 위에 있다는 얘기가 되겠죠.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......! ! \n위...는? 확실히 그곳은 찾아보지 않았어요... 하지만... 만약 정말로 그곳에 있는 거라면... Jackson 씨는 위험해요!</i>\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "위쪽은 Vanessa가 조종하고 있는 로봇들이 있잖아? 지금 그곳으로 들어가버린 거라면...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["PAFF"], "content": "제가 가볼게요! 만일을 위해서라도... 그리고 제겐... 바이러스도 있으니까...\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "Aroma 짱!\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "녀석들 상대로 바이러스를 사용하는 것은 모기를 상대로 칼을 뽑아드는 격입니다. 가능하다면 무탈하게 작전대로 진행했으면 하는 바람이지만.\n아까 그 포메이션으로 가도록 하죠. \n저와 들고양이 씨가 엄호를 맡을 테니,  Miss PAFF는 바이러스를 가지고 이곳에 남아 수색 작업을 펼쳐주시죠.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Nora]"], "content": "<i>......그럼 그렇게 하죠.</i>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["MetalImpact", "물건이 부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "무슨 소리지?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "큰일이다! 바깥을 봐! 대량의 아키텍트가!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["NEKO#ΦωΦ"], "content": "우엑? 으아아? 어, 어떡하지...\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["ConneR"], "content": "휴우...... 최악의 타이밍이군... 아니, 한편으론 나름 괜찮은 타이밍인가... \n2대, 당신이 바깥에 있는 사람들과 협력해서 저들을 막아주셨으면 합니다! 절대로 안으로 들어오게 해선 안 됩니다!\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["JOE"], "content": "알겠어!\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_Reverb", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......아직 멀었어? 벌써 꽤 걸은 것 같은데.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "거의 다 왔어. 바로 이 앞이야.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "만약 Nora에게 네가 OS 공간의 위치를 알려줄 수 있다면, 아마 널 현실로 데리고 갈 수 있는 방법을 생각해낼 수 있을지도 몰라...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "앞전에서도 갇혀있던 Shannon의 의식을 발견한 적이 있었어. 만약 그 아이의 육체를 동일한 장소로 데리고 온다면, 아마도 다시 재연결시킬 수 있을 거라고. 너도 비록 육체는 이미 없어졌지만...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......그렇구나.\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry......이렇게나 많은 일들이 있었는데... 이젠 네게 그걸 얘기해줄 수 없었다는 것에... 나는...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......원래는 네가 구황회에서 제대로 회복하고 나면 말하려고 했었는데...막상 지금 이렇게 널 만나니까 대체 어디서부터 얘기를 해야 할지 갈피를 못잡겠어...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......말해봐.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "나는... 엄청 후회했어... \n그때 널 떠나기로 결정했던 것을... 이 몇 년 동안 계속. 절대로 널 미워해서 그런 결정을 내린 것이 아닌데... 나는... 그것이 내게 주는 벌이라고 생각했어. 옛날에 그 일들을 막지 못했고 곁에 있는 사람을 지켜주지도 못했으니까... 내 자신은 행복할 자격이 없다고 생각했어...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "하지만......너를 소홀히 했던 것이 너를 그렇게 힘들게 할 줄은 정말 생각도 못했었어. 정작 중요한 것은... 아직 살아있는 사람인데... 이제는 알게 됐어.\n너와 함께 했었던 그 시절... 정말 너무 행복했었다. 고마워.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......응, 나도.\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "우리가 반드시 널 여기서 구해낼 방법을 찾아낼게. 이 모든 일이 끝나면, 그때 다시......\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\"><i>X͟͝e͟n̛͜͜͞o̸͢ǹ͘҉͡......Xenon 씨......들리세요......? </i></font>\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......잠깐, 들었어? PAFF의 목소리야! 정말 도착했구나!  \nPAFF! 나다! 들리나!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenon! 드디어 연락이 됐군요! 근처에 너무 강한 신호 간섭이 있어서 그곳으로 갈 수가 없어요! 어쨌든 빨리 그곳에서 나오세요!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "기다려! 여기서 Sherry를 찾았어! 바로 내 앞에 있다고!\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Sherry 씨라니......? 무슨 소릴 하시는 거예요? 그리고 Xenon 씨는 지금... 계속 Library 근처로 다가가고 있어요! Vanessa의 코어 근처에 접근하는 것은 너무 위험하다고요!\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......! ? \n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "지금 대체 뭘 보고 계신지는 모르겠지만, 이곳엔 아키텍트들의 의식 말고는 아무것도 없어요! 빨리 제 목소리가 있는 방향으로 서둘러서 오세요!\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon...... 너도 들었지?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "넘어가선 안 돼. 저건...내가 들었던 목소리랑 똑같아. 항상 각종 방법으로 날 저쪽으로 끌어들이려고 해... 그 목소리가 있는 쪽에 가까워질수록... 강력한 살의가 느껴져.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "큭......\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenon 씨! NEKO 씨도 Neumann 씨도 이젠 더이상 못 버텨요! 접속 시간이 거의 다 끝나가요! 접속이 끊기기 전에 빨리 돌아오지 않으면... 다시는 돌아오지 못하게 될 수도 있어요!\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "가자. 우린 계속 앞으로 가야만 해.\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......Sherry......\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon......? \n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......물어보고 싶은 게 있어. 너는 어떻게... 상황을 알고 있는 거지?\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......뭐? \n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "계속 이곳에 있었다면... 바깥 상황을 알 수 없었을 텐데... 어떻게 우리들이 지금 Node 08의 A.R.C.로비에 있다는 사실을 알고 있는 거지?\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n......지금......그런 얘길 할 때가 아니라고? 지금 빨리 서둘러서......\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Trigger", "총을 꺼낸다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......! ! \n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......대답해.\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Simon......너......나를 못믿는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......크윽......\n"}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[̷̕͠҉̶P̶̕A҉҉̴̨F̢͟͜F̴̀͟]͏̢"], "content": "Xenon 씨! Nora 씨가 간섭 신호를 찾았대요! 바로 Xenon 씨 옆에 있대요! 뭐가 보이든 더 이상 앞으로 가시면